headline: Dell Technologies Rides AI Boom Through Infrastructure Arm
summary: Dell Technologies (DELL) is capitalizing on the surging demand for AI (artificial intelligence) by doubling down on its Infrastructure Solutions Group (ISG). As enterprises race to adopt AI-powered technologies, Dell’s robust portfolio of servers, storage, and networking solutions is playing a pivotal role in powering next-gen workloads.
